admin_log_authenticated_read.name: admin_log_authenticated_read
admin_log_authenticated_read.using: (auth.uid())::text IN (SELECT id FROM users WHERE is_admin = true)

announcements_admin_all.name: announcements_admin_all
announcements_admin_all.using:
exists (
      select 1 from sys_user_roles ur 
      join sys_roles r on ur.role_id = r.id 
      where ur.user_id = ( (select auth.uid()) )::text
      and r.name in ('super_admin', 'admin')
    )
announcements_admin_all.withCheck:
exists (
      select 1 from sys_user_roles ur 
      join sys_roles r on ur.role_id = r.id 
      where ur.user_id = ( (select auth.uid()) )::text
      and r.name in ('super_admin', 'admin')
    )

credentials_owner_read.name: credentials_owner_read
credentials_owner_read.using: ( (select auth.uid()) )::text = (select user_id from volunteer_profiles where id = "credentials"."profile_id")

tenant_invites_admin_all.name: tenant_invites_admin_all
tenant_invites_admin_all.using:
EXISTS (
      SELECT 1 FROM tenant_members tm
      WHERE tm.tenant_id = "tenant_invites"."tenant_id"
        AND tm.user_id = ( (select auth.uid()) )::text
        AND tm.role = 'admin'
    )
tenant_invites_admin_all.withCheck:
EXISTS (
      SELECT 1 FROM tenant_members tm
      WHERE tm.tenant_id = "tenant_invites"."tenant_id"
        AND tm.user_id = ( (select auth.uid()) )::text
        AND tm.role = 'admin'
    )

tenant_members_admin_read.name: tenant_members_admin_read
tenant_members_admin_read.using:
EXISTS (

    )

applications_applicant_read.name: applications_applicant_read
applications_applicant_read.using: ( (select auth.uid()) )::text = (select user_id from volunteer_profiles where id = "volunteer_applications"."applicant_id")
